Client â†’ DNS Query (UDP Port 53) â†’ DNS Server â†’ Returns IP Address
Client â†’ TCP Handshake (Port 80/443) â†’ Web Server
Client â†’ HTTP GET Request â†’ Server Sends HTML
Browser Displays Web Page
ğŸ“ Key Point

First UDP for DNS lookup â†’ Then TCP handshake â†’ Then HTTP/HTTPS request â†’ Server sends HTML
